# Take a plate from the Liconic transfer tray into a carousel site.
#
# Preconditions (operator-enforced):
#   - A plate is physically on the transfer tray.
#   - The target (cassette, position) site is empty.
#
# The server persists the plate_name → (cassette, position) mapping in
# its JSON registry on success. Re-using an already-registered
# plate_name is rejected. Positions are 1-indexed.
string plate_name                       # unique label; rejected if already in use
string barcode                          # optional ("")
uint8 cassette                          # 1-indexed
uint8 position                          # 1-indexed within the cassette
---
bool success
string message
---
string stage                            # "validating" | "dispatching" | "waiting_ready" | "done"
